<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en" dir="ltr">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" name="viewport">
  <meta name="x-apple-disable-message-reformatting">
  <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
  <meta content="telephone=no" name="format-detection">
  <title>Vendors Notification</title>
  <style media="screen" type="text/css">
    #outlook a {
      padding:0;
    }
    .es-button {
      mso-style-priority:100!important;
      text-decoration:none!important;
    }
    a[x-apple-data-detectors] {
      color:inherit!important;
      text-decoration:none!important;
      font-size:inherit!important;
      font-family:inherit!important;
      font-weight:inherit!important;
      line-height:inherit!important;
    }
    [data-ogsb] .es-button {
      border-width:0!important;
      padding:10px 20px 10px 20px!important;
    }
    body {
      background-color: #EDEDED;
      color: #000000;
      font-family: 'helvetica', sans-serif;
      font-size: 0.875rem;
      line-height: 1rem;
      -webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;
      -ms-text-size-adjust: 100%;
      padding: 0;
      margin: 0;
    }
    .wrapper {
      background-color: #FFFFFF;
      max-width: 640px;
      padding: 32px;
      Margin: 0 auto;
    }
    img {
      max-width: 100%;
    }
    .heading-text-main {
      color: #000000;
      font-weight: bold;
      font-size: 14px;
      line-height: 16px;
    }
    .heading-text {
      color: #000000;
      font-weight: bold;
      font-size: 12px;
      line-height: 14px;
    }
    .sub-text {
      font-weight: normal;
      font-size: 10px;
      line-height: 11px;
      color: #000000;
    }
    .count-border {
      border: 1px solid #D9D9D9;
      padding: 6px 8px;
    }
    .small-text {
      font-weight: normal;
      font-size: 8px;
      line-height: 9px;
    }
    .lebel-text {
      font-weight: normal;
      font-size: 10px;
      line-height: 11px;
    }
    /* css start for multi vendors*/
    .email-header {
      padding-top: 20px;
      text-align: center;
      width: 100%;
    }
    .email-header .email-logo {
      width: 172px;
    }
    .email-header .email-heading {
      color: #000;
      font-size: 24px;
      font-weight: 400;
      line-height: 28px;
      letter-spacing: 0.01em;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .msg-wrapper {
      padding: 1.5rem;
    }
    p {
      margin-top: 0;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }
    .btns-wrapper {
      display: flex;
      align-items: flex-start;
      padding-top: 0.5rem;
      padding-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }
    .btns-wrapper .btn {
      padding: 17px 20px 13px;
      height: auto;
      font-size: 0.75rem;
      line-height: 0.875rem;
      letter-spacing: 1.25px;
      text-decoration: none;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }
    .btns-wrapper .btn:hover,
    .btns-wrapper .btn:focus {
      text-decoration: underline;
    }
    .btns-wrapper .btn.btn-view-order {
      margin-right: 1rem;
    }
    .btns-wrapper .btn.btn-primary {
      background-color: #212322;
      color: #fff;
    }
    .btns-wrapper .btn.btn-transparent {
      background-color: transparent;
      color: #212322;
    }
    .border-bottom-grey {
      border-bottom: 0.5px solid #D9D9D9;
    }
    .table-container {
      padding-top: 1.5rem;
      overflow-x: auto;
    }
    .section-heading {
      color: #212322;
      font-size: 1rem;
      font-weight: 400;
      line-height: 1.125rem;
      margin: auto;
    }
    .table-container table td {
      border-bottom: 0.5px solid #e0e0e0;
      color: #374151;
      padding-top: 1rem;
      padding-bottom: 0.75rem;
      vertical-align: middle;
    }
    .table-container .pro-name-cont {
      padding-left: 29px;
    }
    .table-container tbody .sub-desc {
      color: #6B7280;
      font-size: 0.75rem;
      line-height: 0.875rem;
      padding-top: 0.375rem;
    }
    .totals-wrapper {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: flex-end;
      padding-top: 1rem;
    }
    .totals-wrapper .totals-inner-cont {
      color: #455263;
      width: 70%;
      max-width: 305px;
    }
    .totals-wrapper .totals-inner-cont td {
      padding-bottom: 0.8125rem;
    }
    .totals-wrapper .totals-inner-cont .bordered-col {
      border-bottom: 1px solid #e9e7e7;
    }
    .totals-wrapper .totals-inner-cont .grand-total {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
    }
    .address-wrapper {
      background: #FCFCFC;
      border: 0.5px solid #D9D9D9;
      border-radius: 4px;
      color: #6d6d6d;
      padding: 1rem;
      margin-top: 0.75rem;
    }
    .address-wrapper-faq {
      padding-right: 52px;
    }
    .address-wrapper-faq .address-title {
      color: #212322;
      font-size: 12px;
    }
    .address-wrapper-faq .address-desc {
      color: #757575;
      font-size: 12px;
    }
    .address-title {
      color: #000;
    }
    .notes {
      color: #999;
      font-size: 0.75rem;
      line-height: 0.875rem;
    }
    .sys-gen-note {
      border-bottom: 0.5px solid #e0e0e0;
      color: #757575;
    }
    .social-links-cont {
      padding-top: 27px;
      padding-bottom: 19px;
    }
    .social-links-cont a:not(:last-child) {
      margin-right: 30px;
    }
    .email-footer-copyright {
      color: #6d6d6d;
      font-size: 0.75rem;
      line-height: 1.125rem;
    }
    .color-black {
      color: #000 !important;
    }
    .pt-2 {
      padding-top: 0.5rem !important;
    }
    .pt-3 {
      padding-top: 1rem !important;
    }
    .pt-4 {
      padding-top: 1.5rem !important;
    }
    .py-4 {
      padding-top: 1.5rem !important;
      padding-bottom: 1.5rem !important;
    }
    .pr-3 {
      padding-right: 1rem !important;
    }
    .pt-13 {
      padding-top: 0.8125rem !important;
    }
    .pb-0 {
      padding-bottom: 0 !important;
    }
    .pb-3 {
      padding-bottom: 1rem !important;
    }
    .pb-4 {
      padding-bottom: 1.5rem !important;
    }
    .text-center {
      text-align: center !important;
    }
    .text-right {
      text-align: right !important;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="wrapper">
  <div class="email-header">
    <img src="https://static.techsembly.com/ZAi3VLPw1yHGxEnQpX6TXJ1p" class="email-logo" alt="logo" width="172" height="100"/>
    <h2 class="email-heading">Your Digital Voucher Details</h2>
  </div>
  <div class="msg-wrapper">
    <div class="msg-top border-bottom-grey">
      <p>Dear {{bill_address.firstname}} {{bill_address.lastname}},</p>
      <p>Thanks again for shopping with us. Your order has now been shipped.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="delivery-section pt-4">
      <h4 class="section-heading color-black">Billing Address</h4>
      <div class="address-wrapper">
        <div class="address-title">{{bill_address.firstname}} {{bill_address.lastname}}</div>
        <div class="address-desc">{{ bill_address.address1 }},
          {{#if bill_address.address2}}
          {{ bill_address.address2 }},
          {{/if}}
          {{#if bill_address.apartment_no}}
          {{ bill_address.apartment_no }},
          {{/if}}
          {{#if bill_address.city}}
          {{ bill_address.city }},
          {{/if}}
          {{#if bill_address.state_name}}
          {{ bill_address.state_name }},
          {{/if}}
          {{#if bill_address_country}}
          {{ bill_address_country }},
          {{/if}}
          {{#if bill_address.region}}
          {{ bill_address.region }},
          {{/if}}
          {{#if bill_address.zipcode}}
          {{ bill_address.zipcode }},
          {{/if}}
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="table-container">
      <h4 class="section-heading">Voucher Details</h4>
      <table width="100%" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">
        <thead>
        <tr>
          <th id="pro-img" width="83"></th>
          <th id="pro-name" width="187"></th>
          <th id="qty-ship" width="100"></th>
          <th id="price" width="182"></th>
        </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
        <tr>
          <td class="pro-img-cont">
            <img src="{{line_item.image_url}}" alt="pro-img" width="83"/>
          </td>
          <td class="pro-name-cont">
            <div class="col-head">{{line_item.product_name}}</div>
          </td>
          <td class="pro-qty-cont text-center">
            <div class="col-head">Qty:1</div>
            <div class="sub-desc pt-2">{{line_item.sub_total}}</div>
          </td>
          <td class="pro-price-cont text-right">
            {{line_item.sub_total}}
          </td>
        </tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </div>
    <div class="totals-wrapper">
      <div class="totals-inner-cont">
        <table width="100%" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">
          <thead>
          <tr>
            <th id="price-desc" width="60%"></th>
            <th id="price-amt" width="40%"></th>
          </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody>
          <tr>
            <td class="pr-3">Send to</td>
            <td class="text-right">{{recipient_email}}</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td class="pr-3">Gift Card Message:</td>
            <td>{{message}}</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td class="pr-3">Voucher Value:</td>
            <td class="text-right">{{line_item.sub_total}}</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td class="pr-3 bordered-col">Estimated Sales Tax:</td>
            <td class="text-right bordered-col">{{sales_tax}}</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td class="pt-13 pr-3 pb-0">Grand Total:</td>
            <td class="pt-13 text-right pb-0 grand-total">{{grand_total}}</td>
          </tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="billing-section pt-4">
      <div class="address-wrapper-faq">
        <div class="address-title">How do I return my order?</div>
        <div class="address-desc pb-3">You can return your item(s) within 7 days of purchase and 14 days for Capella. Check the return steps <a href="#" style="color: #757575;">here.</a></div>
        <div class="address-title">What is Capella refund policy & timelines?</div>
        <div class="address-desc pb-3">Refund timelines are different for each payment method. You can check the refund policy <a href="#" style="color: #757575;">here.</a></div>
        <div class="address-title">I found the package open and seal broken. What should I do?</div>
        <div class="address-desc pb-3">You are advised to not accept delivery of such orders. However, if you do receive any such package, please get in touch with us immediately via support.</div>
        <div class="address-title">Where do I find the invoice of my order?</div>
        <div class="address-desc pb-3">A hard copy of the invoice should always be sent along with your order.</div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="py-4">
    </div>
    <div class="sys-gen-note pb-4">
      This is a system generated message. Please do not reply.
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="email-footer">
    <div class="social-links-cont text-center">
      <a href="https://www.instagram.com/capellabangkok/" target="_blank"><img src="https://static.techsembly.com/y9GmmRooddrjN2GGuJR6mM3E" width="17" alt="instagram"/></a>
      <a href="https://www.facebook.com/CapellaBangkok" target="_blank"><img src="https://static.techsembly.com/EmUTgngqVeGmqHoXTSvgcRYa" width="17" alt="fb"/></a>
      <a href="https://page.line.me/capellabangkok" target="_blank"><img src="https://static.techsembly.com/neeimCVGBZEBdV8tLSSDLQse" width="17" alt="line"/></a>
    </div>
    <div class="footer-logo-cont text-center">
      <a href="#"><img src="https://static.techsembly.com/VCANzXL6tkpsHBg172e8t8rd" width="123" alt=""></a>
    </div>
    <div class="email-footer-copyright text-center pt-3 pb-4">
      Copyright Â© 2021<br>
      Capella Hotel Group.<br>
      South of some city, Road 57, Bangkok.
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>
